                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Trail of the Qilin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/20/35428890/67d6f9d70e695a791caa42953d11e1e3_7923398575412106540.png",
                "id": "talent21404",
                "key": "Frostflake Arrow",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Frostflake Arrow"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sacred Cryo Pearl</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/30/35428890/6b78c979575a782c1625dce67992cf90_6743611143073519014.png",
                "id": "talent8165",
                "key": "Celestial Shower",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Celestial Shower"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG </span>to all opposing characters on standby.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/11/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_929897109187337777.png",
                "id": "talent1020",
                "key": "Sacred Cryo Pearl",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/11/35428890/5768b83a04afeb8e581b0f7864fd39d9_2020195863022109967.png",
                "title": "Sacred Cryo Pearl"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/11/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_927810827928561880.png",
                "id": "talent71109",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bounses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4667047790094514977.png",
